/www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/roy-keane-neil-diamond-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/roy-keane-neil-diamond-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/roy-keane-neil-diamond-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>罗伊·基恩（Roy Keane）曾经在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neil-diamond">尼尔·戴蒙德（Neil Diamond）</a>的音乐会上与某人发生“争吵”，因为他在他旁边演唱了《甜蜜的卡罗琳》（Sweet Caroline）。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-best-football-songs-7388">在他们自己的联盟​​中：最好的足球歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>最近，记者、作家兼体育广播员马克·普格奇 (Mark Pougatch) 又重述了这则轶事，他曾与基恩一起在 ITV 工作，报道 2021 年举行的 2020 年欧洲杯。</p><p>当英格兰队进入决赛并最终在点球大战中以 3-2 输给意大利队时，戴蒙德的 1969 年热门歌曲转变为体育歌曲再次风靡全国。</p><p>普加奇在最近一集 <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/5oIOFQHnNx9VsGGsHze07X" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人生目标</em></a>》播客中回忆起那一刻时，他反思了这首歌的再次复兴。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> “罗伊去过尼尔·戴蒙德的音乐会……”</p><p> “是的，大约10年前。我最终和旁边的女人发生了争执——她一直大声唱歌，所以那天晚上我遇到了一些麻烦。但音乐会太精彩了！” <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f923.png" alt="🤣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>经典罗伊·基恩<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f606.png" alt="😆" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ITVFootball?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ITV足球</a>| <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Euro2020?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Euro2020</a> <a href="https://t.co/TH8G9KSKdr">pic.twitter.com/TH8G9KSKdr</a></p><p> - ITV Football (@itvfootball) <a href="https://twitter.com/itvfootball/status/1412835020746674179?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2021 年 7 月 7 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “真正有趣的是，当人群开始唱《甜蜜的卡罗琳》时，赖蒂也在唱，”他说。</p><p>他随后回忆起曼联传奇人物兼足球评论员基恩透露，就在英格兰队与丹麦队进行半决赛之前，他曾在十多年前的演出中与一位女士交换了心声，因为她给英格兰队唱了这首歌。大声打。</p><p> “然后突然间，加里·内维尔突然说，‘罗伊，你喜欢尼尔·戴蒙德’。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="尼尔·戴蒙德 - 甜蜜的卡罗琳（音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4F_RCWVoL4s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “And Roy goes, &#39;Yeah I went to a Neil Diamond concert – I had a row with the woman next door to me because she was repeating all the lyrics.</p><p> “I&#39;m like, &#39;Roy, you can&#39;t have a row with someone at a Neil Diamond concert, for Christ&#39;s sake!&#39;”</p><p> In the <a href="https://twitter.com/itvfootball/status/1412835020746674179?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1412835020746674179%7Ctwgr%5E6180c41f1bbdbf1adb0ac0a64dd7a303acbae5d6%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticle-9766039%2FEuro-2020-Roy-Keane-reveals-rowed-woman-Neil-Diamond-concert-hilarious-anecdote.html">original broadcast</a> , Keane said that he “ended up in a bit of trouble that night”, but added that it was a “brilliant concert”.</p><p> Back in December 2022, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-diamond-comes-out-of-retirement-to-sing-sweet-caroline-on-broadway-3362337">Diamond came out of retirement to sing &#39;Sweet Caroline&#39;</a> during the curtain call of a new Broadway musical about his life.</p><p> The singer announced his retirement from touring <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-diamond-parkinsons-disease-diagnosis-touring-retirement-2226400">in 2018 after being diagnosed with Parkinson&#39;s disease</a> , though <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-diamond-makes-rare-public-appearance-and-sings-sweet-caroline-3251015">made a rare appearance earlier in 2022 at a Boston Red Sox game</a> to perform the hit.</p><p> In April this year, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-diamond-was-in-denial-about-parkinsons-diagnosis-for-years-3424463">he opened up about living with Parkinson&#39;s disease in a new interview</a> . “I don&#39;t like it but this is me. This is what I have to accept. And I&#39;m willing to do it,” Diamond told <em><a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/neil-diamond-on-coming-to-terms-with-his-parkinsons-diagnosis/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CBS</a></em> . “Okay, so this is the hand that God&#39;s given me, and I have to make the best of it, and so I am.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roy-keane-once-got-in-row-with-woman-at-neil-diamond-concert-singing-sweet-caroline-3482666">Roy Keane once got in “a row” with woman at Neil Diamond concert for singing &#39;Sweet Caroline&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
