blank" rel="noopener">Visit here</a> for tickets and check out the full list of tour dates below. </p><figure id="attachment_3482683" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3482683" style="width: 1000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3482683" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Death-Cult-Tour-poster.jpg" alt="Death Cult Tour poster. Credit: PRESS" width="1000" height="1298" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Death-Cult-Tour-poster.jpg 1000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Death-Cult-Tour-poster-400x519.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Death-Cult-Tour-poster-800x1038.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Death-Cult-Tour-poster-696x903.jpg 696w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3482683" class="wp-caption-text"> Death Cult Tour poster. Credit: PRESS</figcaption></figure><h2> <strong>Death Cult – &#39;Death Cult 8323&#39; tour dates are:</strong></h2><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>23 – Los Angeles, CA , The Theatre at The Ace Hotel</strong></p><p><strong>十一月</strong><br /><strong>6 – Belfast, UK, Telegraph</strong><br /> <strong>7 – Dublin, IE, 3Olympia</strong><br /> <strong>9 – Sheffield, UK, Foundry</strong><br /> <strong>10 – Liverpool, UK, Guild of Students</strong><br /> <strong>12 – Glasgow, UK, Barrowland</strong><br /> <strong>13 – Nottingham, UK, Rock City</strong><br /> <strong>14 – Birmingham, UK, O2 Institute</strong><br /> <strong>16 – Bournemouth, UK, O2 Academy</strong><br /> <strong>17 – Norwich, UK, UEA</strong><br /> <strong>18 – Manchester, UK, Albert Hall</strong><br /> <strong>20 – London, UK, Brixton Electric</strong><br /> <strong>21 – London, UK, Brixton Electric</strong></p><p> Last year, The Cult <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cult-share-single-a-cut-inside-unveil-track-listing-for-under-the-midnight-sun-3307512">released their 11th studio album &#39;Under the Midnight Sun&#39;</a> . They also announced a US tour is set to kick off in October.</p><p> Speaking about the creation of the LP, Astbury discussed how the global pandemic impacted the creative process behind &#39;Under The Midnight Sun&#39;. “When the world stopped, I had this moment to write in real time, to calculate,” he said. “I was compelled by this vision, this anomaly, this memory, of being under the midnight sun. [Producer Tom Dalgety] helped us bring a new musical shape and frequency to our process.”</p><p> View the full itinerary and ticket details for The Cult&#39;s US tour <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fthe-cult-tickets%2Fartist%2F1440075%3Firgwc%3D1%26clickid%3D0prTtizx%253AxyNTutXHCVhR2q4UkDW3M1hI08k1c0%26camefrom%3DCFC_BUYAT_1882189%26impradid%3D1882189%26REFERRAL_ID%3Dtmfeedbuyat1882189%26wt.mc_id%3Daff_BUYAT_1882189%26utm_source%3D1882189-Consequence%26impradname%3DConsequence%26utm_medium%3Daffiliate%26ircid%3D4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/death-cult-announce-uk-us-and-ireland-tour-in-celebration-of-40th-anniversary-3482641">Death Cult announce UK, US and Ireland tour in celebration of 40th anniversary</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
